* [MetObs_GUI](https://github.com/vergauwenthomas/MetObs_GUI): A graphical user interface for the MetObs-toolkit
* [JOSS publication on the MetObs-toolkit](https://joss.theoj.org/papers/10.21105/joss.05916#)

